        "subject": "LU-18548 tests: ensure sanity/160f GC has started",
        "message": "LU-18548 tests: ensure sanity/160f GC has started\n\nWhen waiting for the \"idle\" changelog user to be removed, wait a\nfew seconds for the process to start.  Otherwise it is possible\nthat the GC thread hasn't yet started when the test is checking\nfor it to have completed, which causes intermittent test failures.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nChange-Id: Id75386abb581ad2ea2f3d79a6999d3d0626cf876\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/64924\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Bruno Faccini <bfaccini@nvidia.com>\nReviewed-by: Mikhail Pershin <mpershin@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
